The  preferences folder is [APPLICATION-DATA-FOLDER]/com.oxygenxml[APPLICATION-DATA-FOLDER]/com.oxygenxml.author>[APPLICATION-DATA-FOLDER]/com.oxygenxml.developer, where
            [APPLICATION-DATA-FOLDER] is:

